Why Choose Jet Park
Why Choose Jet Park
Why Choose Jet Park
WHY CHOOSE JET PARK?
Wide Range of Activities
We are a well-established park with a wealth of activities. You can stay as busy or relax as much as you want. Do you want to learn shuffleboard? We have a club for that. Enjoy the pool? Of-course we have a pool. Play cards? Yes, we have lots of card groups. We like to celebrate everything. How about putting up a community Christmas Tree with cookies and hot chocolate. Let’s throw in a golf cart and bike parade. Oh yes! Meal Deals every Wednesday for those who don’t want to cook yet another dinner. Nearly every holiday celebration has a meal or potluck for fellowship and fun. We have a club that does cooking demos and a club that’s set up to teach crafts. If you have an interest, we have others to join you doing it.
We have Pickle Ball courts near the park and have started a Pickle Ball Club. If you’d rather just play on your own, no problem. There’s a water Taxi scheduling rides from Bradenton to Anna Marie Island Beaches if you don’t have your own boat. If kayaking is your jam, we’ve got extra kayaks for you to use while you visit Jet Park
